---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About ProofLabs - Independent Credit Card Reviews"
  description="Learn about ProofLabs' mission to provide unbiased, data-driven credit card reviews and comparisons."
>
  <div class="container-custom" style="padding: 8rem 0 6rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text);">
        About ProofLabs
      </h1>
      
      <div style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          ProofLabs was founded on a simple principle: credit card reviews should be driven by data, not advertising dollars.
        </p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          We analyze over 200 credit cards using a comprehensive methodology that evaluates rewards rates, annual fees, sign-up bonuses, and real-world value. Every recommendation is backed by objective analysis and transparent criteria.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Our Mission
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          To help consumers make informed credit card decisions through independent, data-driven analysis. We believe in transparency, accuracy, and putting reader value first.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Our Approach
        </h2>
        
        <ul style="margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>Data-Driven:</strong> We analyze real numbers, not marketing claims</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>Independent:</strong> Our rankings aren't influenced by affiliate relationships</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>Transparent:</strong> We clearly disclose how we make money and how we review</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>Updated Daily:</strong> Credit card offers change frequently—our reviews reflect current rates</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Editorial Standards
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          Our editorial team follows strict guidelines to ensure accuracy and objectivity. We regularly update our reviews, verify all data points, and maintain independence from card issuers.
        </p>
        
        <div style="background-color: var(--color-secondary-bg); border-left: 4px solid #0284c7; padding: 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-secondary-dark);">
            Have questions? <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--color-secondary); text-decoration: underline;">Contact us</a> or read our <a href="/methodology" style="color: var(--color-secondary); text-decoration: underline;">methodology</a> to learn more about how we review credit cards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
